Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白啊　老师  这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能稍微难了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对她说成人的话　她也还是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当小孩啊　妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师　今晚是满月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊　老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢　这种光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看不见但能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯上我们的人潜了进来是毫无疑问的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上面的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也变得有名了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银还真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就只有那点能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴唇的血色似乎不是非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升0.01钠的浓度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该是标准数值啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掌握好个体差别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要光依赖显示屏和计量器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体也好心灵也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　他的嘴好像在说梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做了梦之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是灵媒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认他们不会做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　说不定还是会看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平静的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石崎主任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡回的观测灵的动向有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复数的灵光被拖向特定的坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了让你不要随便出门的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把他干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他一直在打探
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标的成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是他们上面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被要求调查的是他们的成员构成和来历
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞清楚他们的能力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了　灵媒们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让观测灵都回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…他们回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能猜测他们被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CY463有动作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:07:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉观测灵的契约者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间意识被连接了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和放出观测灵的DOLL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么很好的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙　出乎意料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和目标中的一个连接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你能找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找这女孩就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厄…Can you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过外国人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　Mr　卡西特…卡西特…卡西特…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡斯提内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯·卡斯提内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　卡斯提内先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你眼光真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名的钢琴家特地从北欧远道而来指名我这久良泽凯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么没听说啊老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然在外国那么有名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes　凯　久良泽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese most famous detective　大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯…凯　久良泽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说是凯…凯　久良泽　有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真冷静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到线索了吧　不行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能只用一个DOLL就能引他们出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的冲击只要不恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一定在某处徘徊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像梦游一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游刃有余嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来　有烟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能吸这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹也是歌手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是在纽约第三戏剧界的舞台上站过的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是一群演员中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一到时候没有我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是代价嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在写什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女　白色的夜　湖水与愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人淡淡沉入帷幕之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身边只有缥缈的银色月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很优雅的代价嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点像少女向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要多借鉴一下应该会写得更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说勉强人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没写过诗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是件好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说明　你也还有颗活着的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和银无法取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨晚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说她逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOLL不可能按照自己的意愿行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只被植入了仅为了生存而行动的最低限度的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织的人被杀了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是昨晚说的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入的那些家伙干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银也有可能被他们绑架了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺走我们的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有感情　但是记忆却不坏　被抓到了反而不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织的行动就是因为预测到这点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样　包括我们的监视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的结果是DOLL就算被弄坏扔掉也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　你挡路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了　走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厄　那个傻侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要开始到处打听一下  琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么　请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然说那么…　你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过我有急事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去找朋友路上顺便陪你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样　那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探　是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道理由　但他似乎在找银
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了　如果他们有行动就通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我跟着他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们打过照面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那脸很常见　别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs38\fscx75}第十三话     银色之夜、心在水面不曾摇摆…（前篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常出色噢　琪尔西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下面…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　只是弄丢了手电而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　那我去开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要　这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪尔西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗　手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是角色搞错了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让那个灯光活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字写在笔记本上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作品里明明是狼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说不要把原创的东西交给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧　是那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是饮料店　不用那么小家子气地喝也行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很阴沉嘛　那是你的性格设定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是被骗了　稍微笑笑怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看　像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看　这不是来劲了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先固定外表是基本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是Cosplay也好其他的也好都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微离开下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的时候帮我带杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己去拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都问了是哪里的快餐厅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有更容易理解的路标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转角那有动画店  从那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AA制的哦  琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被自己的观测灵吸引了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我预想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以呼唤DOLL的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃　银
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙　黑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塌了　黑　快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能躲远点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪尔西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪尔西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪尔西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔达　你想连我也杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事　没有吞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了吗　这是代价
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪尔西　是我　艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的　现在正在进行调查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们藏起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到出国前为止就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是想打探什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么她会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道在被人追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人追　被谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我无法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟踪狂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　跟踪狂？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经闹得那么大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然跟着那么可爱的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪尔西　来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想让你穿穿看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋　又不是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我会尽可能给予谢礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了　骑虎难下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是说藏起来究竟哪里才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是要去一次的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一次什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪可会加油的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让敌人逃掉了　而且银也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次找到她的时候不管情况如何　都把银干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下　黄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们现在闹矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才真是中了敌人的下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼　别把我当你们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和你们相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有想过和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难看地恐惧着发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种不像样的感情我们契约者没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了　把银干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说不干的话　就由我来干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要跟来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人偷闲是很狡猾的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在做保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我介绍你温泉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琪尔西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平静下来了就回去吧　琪尔西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列车没有终点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细密着降下的雨　照出隐藏着的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颤抖的心　毫不摇动的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.07,0:23:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还在渴求那些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同银色月光一起消失的日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼瞳中映射不出的那些光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的确能传达到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.43,0:24:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85\pos(440,350)\fs42}{\b0}第十四话\N银色之夜、心在水面不曾摇摆…（后篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:14.30,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}蓝蓝的　蓝蓝的　天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:19.73,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:25.13,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甜甜的　淡淡的　沉重的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:29.97,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被这些拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:35.90,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在这月光下 无人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:40.72,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有呼唤着你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:46.44,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都在寻找着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:51.04,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在这光芒中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:56.90,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}什么都抓不住的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:01.97,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无时无刻不牵挂着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.07,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我没有停止想念的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:14.87,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷惘的心　希望能传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:19.57,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在这月光下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:25.07,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}请呼唤我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:31.47,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我一定会去见你　无论你在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:37.87,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在这光芒中


